The Eridian Crossbow
Replaces Longbow

A crossbow, rebuilt with eridian technology
i can say it's helluva lot stronger than a normal crossbow

Single shot mag
Consumes 3 ammo per shot
Shots pierces enemies
Shots pierces through shields
The crossbow is lighter than usual weapons and you can move 110% faster
Insane accuracy
High velocity
Very slow arrow regeneration
Very slow reload
High damage
100% Elemental chance
x2 Damage on critical hit
Arrows are much higher caliber vs bullets
Better sniper than an actual sniper rifle


Can spawn with slag elemental
Slag weapon code BL2(hwAAAACWkwCAaIRBDAEFFIBRAAMNhhcMBZgcMP////8zg2FBQg3m)


Iridium in the weapon description is not a typo, it fires iridium arrows, not eridian arrows.


